data.title: Public Health Forum Series (Final)
data.meta_description: Public Health Forum Series (Final) - Free download as PDF File (.pdf), Text File (.txt) or read online for free. The document announces a series of events from June 10th to 14th hosted by Drs. Christina Parks and Elizabeth Mumper on topics related to COVID-19, immunization, children's health, and achieving optimal family health. The events will take place at various venues and include presentations, panels, and sessions for health professionals. Registration information is provided to attend the events being held to discuss the impact of health issues on children and families.
